{"type":null,"faqId":9768,"title":"荣耀畅玩版（g750-t01）如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>设置</b></span><span> <span>&gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">安全</span></b><span> <span>&gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">屏幕锁定</span></b><span><span> &gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图案</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>在“选择您的图案”界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击“继续”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置图案解锁时，设置的线条至少要包含</span><span><span>4</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个圆点才是有效图案。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img style=\"width:229px;height:481px;\" height=\"539\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30272\" width=\"222\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击“确认”完成解锁图形的设置。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30271\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"383","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"p